ai_prompts.prompt_content:
Extract comprehensive earnings data for {symbol} including:
- Most recent quarterly/annual earnings report (last 4 quarters preferred)
- EPS (actual vs estimated, YoY growth)
- Revenue (actual vs estimated, YoY growth)
- Operating margins, net margins
- Forward guidance (revenue, EPS ranges)
- Key business segment performance
- Management commentary highlights
- Next earnings date and expectations

Return structured JSON:
{
  "earnings_data": {
    "latest_quarter": {
      "date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
      "period": "QX YYYY",
      "revenue": {"actual": X, "estimated": X, "yoy_growth": X},
      "eps": {"actual": X.XX, "estimated": X.XX, "yoy_growth": X},
      "margins": {"operating": X.X, "net": X.X},
      "guidance": {"revenue_low": X, "revenue_high": X, "eps_low": X.XX, "eps_high": X.XX}
    },
    "previous_quarters": [...],
    "key_insights": ["insight1", "insight2"],
    "next_earnings": {"date": "YYYY-MM-DD", "expectations": "brief description"}
  }
}

Extract recent market news and sentiment for {symbol} including:
- Breaking news (last 24-48 hours priority)
- Analyst ratings and price target changes
- Major developments (products, partnerships, regulatory)
- Market sentiment indicators
- Competitor news affecting {symbol}
- Macroeconomic factors impacting the stock

Focus on actionable insights, not generic market updates. Filter out noise and prioritize material events.

Return structured JSON:
{
  "news_data": {
    "breaking_news": [
      {
        "headline": "headline text",
        "source": "source",
        "timestamp": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM",
        "sentiment": "positive|negative|neutral",
        "impact": "high|medium|low",
        "summary": "1-2 sentence summary of key points"
      }
    ],
    "analyst_updates": [
      {
        "firm": "firm name",
        "rating": "buy|hold|sell",
        "price_target": X,
        "previous_target": X,
        "timestamp": "YYYY-MM-DD",
        "reasoning": "brief explanation"
      }
    ],
    "key_developments": ["development1", "development2"],
    "overall_sentiment": "positive|negative|neutral",
    "last_updated": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM"
  }
}
